==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Misproportion
<hw>Mis`pro*por"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To give
wrong or unesthetic proportions to; to join without due proportion;
<as>as, the legs were <ex>misrpoportioned</ex> to the
body</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>misproportion</ent>⟦br⟧

